title: Rams/Chiefs Banger and Thanksgiving Preview Show
itunes:title: Rams/Chiefs Banger and Thanksgiving Preview Show
description:
A room filled with heroes- Dan Hanzus, Chris Wesseling, Marc Sessler and Gregg Rosenthal recap the Monday night thriller where the Los Angeles Rams beat the Kansas City Chiefs. (00:00). The heroes then preview all three games to be played on Thanksgiving. (15:45)
